<entry level="2" type="bullet">

Shifting role of the state in social policy (e.g. federal/provincial responsibilities, focus on the “fiscal imbalance,” etc.)</entry>
<entry level="2" type="bullet">

Changing relationships with all levels of government </entry>
<entry level="2" type="bullet">

Changing <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../763/75763.xml">
provincial</link> government priorities (greater challenges to put poverty on the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../920/3605920.xml">
